  Game information :
  ==================

  Based on the real-life obstacles faced by the men of the American 8th Air
  Force, B-17 Gunner: Air War Over Germany features authentic, fast-paced
  action! Repel furious enemy attacks as you fly 25 dangerous daylight bombing
  missions - the same number flown by American crews before being rotated home.
  Defend your B-17 against five different types of realistically rendered
  Luftwaffe aircraft and listen to intercom chatter, droning engines, screaming
  bombs and other authentic combat sounds.

  Game Features :
  ===============

  - Engage in high altitude 3D combat

  - Control six .50-caliber machine gun positions and a Norden bombsight

  - Defend your B-17 against realistically rendered Luftwaffe aircraft

  - Take battle damage, lose gun positions

  - Listen to intercom chatter, droning engines, screaming bombs and other
    realistic sounds


